# 枚举与字典 Demo API 测试

### ===== 查询接口 =====

### 1. 获取所有枚举列表
GET http://localhost:5000/api/enums

### 2. 获取指定枚举（OrderStatus）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/enums/OrderStatus

### 3. 获取指定枚举（PaymentMethod）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/enums/PaymentMethod

### 4. 获取单个用户（字典翻译：性别、民族）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/user

### 5. 获取用户列表（批量字典翻译）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/users

### 6. 获取单个订单（枚举 + 字典 + 嵌套对象翻译）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/order

### 7. 获取订单列表（批量嵌套翻译）
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/orders

### ===== 写入接口（含校验）=====

### 8. 创建订单（枚举字符串/数字均可接收）
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/create-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderNo": "ORD-2026-100",
    "amount": 199.99,
    "status": "Paid",
    "paymentMethod": "WeChatPay",
    "source": "app"
}

### 9. 创建订单 - 数字枚举值
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/create-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderNo": "ORD-2026-101",
    "amount": 299.99,
    "status": 1,
    "paymentMethod": 2,
    "source": "pc"
}

### 10. 创建订单 - 无效来源（应返回400）
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/create-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderNo": "ORD-ERR",
    "amount": 99,
    "status": "Pending",
    "paymentMethod": "Alipay",
    "source": "invalid_source"
}

### 11. 创建用户（字典值自动校验）
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/create-user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "赵六",
    "sex": "1",
    "nation": "4",
    "age": 30,
    "email": "zhaoliu@test.com"
}

### ===== 校验接口 =====

### 12. 校验字典值是否合法
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/validate-dict-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "dictCode": "sex",
    "dictValue": "1"
}

### 13. 校验枚举值（名称）- 不区分大小写
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/validate-enum
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "enumName": "OrderStatus",
    "enumValue": "Paid"
}

### 14. 校验枚举值（数字）
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/validate-enum
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "enumName": "OrderStatus",
    "enumValue": "0"
}

### 15. 校验枚举值（非法值应返回400）
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/validate-enum
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "enumName": "OrderStatus",
    "enumValue": "invalid_status"
}

### 16. 刷新字典缓存
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/refresh-cache